title: Neffarious in the Northwest
description: The Neff Skateboarding Team got together for their first ever road trip to film "Neffarious in the Northwest." This epic edit with Thrasher Magazine features Neff Skateboarding Team riders Aaron "Jaws" Homoki, Dakota Servold, Matt Bennett, Leo Romero, Nick Merlino, Silas Baxter-Neal, and Derrick Wilson (not in this edit: Moose.) Enjoy!
